resources.string:
Android Series app:
 Widget
 Transparent dark background with white text
 Stored locally / On GDrive?
 Elements:
 Title
 Season (with +)
 Episode (with +)
 More info
 Can set a few things on element creation
 Episode Count type:
 S_x E_y
 E_yyy
 Title
 Extra Info (Like where you watch it)
 Episode count resets to 0 when pressing Season+
 Hold on Episode or Season to enter manually
 Swipe on element to mark as finished watching
 Added to list at bottom with a divider in bold text
 Can swipe to add back to top (and remembers S+E)
 If new season is announced or whatnot
 Swipe up/down to scroll through list

 List Object
 List of ListElements

 List Element Object
 string title
 uint season
 uint episode
 string extraInfo
 bool isFinished;
 void IterateEpisode();
 episode++;
 void IterateSeason();
 season++;
 episode = 0;
 void Initialize(title, extraInfo = null);
 this.title = title;
 if (extraInfo != null) this.exInfo = exInfo;
 episode = 0;
 season = 0;
 void Finish();
 isFinished = true;
 void UnFinish();
 isFinished = false;





