//         Contains a mutable ExtraInfo text
//       Contains a clickable Season area
//         Contains an immutable S char
//         Contains an immutable ___ line
//         Contains a mutable number
//       Contains a clickable Episode area
//         Contains an immutable E char
//         Contains an immutable ___ line
//         Contains a mutable number

//     Card E
//       Contains a clickable image (checkmark when unfinished, square when finished)
//       Contains a clickable text area
//         Contains a mutable Title text
//         Contains a mutable ExtraInfo text
//       Contains a clickable Episode area
//         Contains an immutable E char
